About this item

  • Great Way to Store All Your Hats: The hanging hat organizer is consist of 5 clear wide pockets with 5 sturdy plate on the bottom. You can see all your hats on the hat rack and they won' t fall out when removing or placing a different hat.
  • Large Capacity for 50-60 Hats: The size of the baseball cap holder is 16*7*51inch. The deep pockets apply for multiple hats and each pocket has enough room to hold 10-12 caps. The cap holder is a great space saver.
  • Save Your Time And Space: The clear PVC window and large open design make it easy for you to select hats you want and take them out. So the hat holder can save your time. And the hat rack for door can keep the hats neat and tidy without taking up too much space.
  • 3 Hooks Fit Standard Doors: Hat rack for baseball caps is equipped with 3 hooks fit standard door. They can be hung on the bedroom door, closet door, pantry door and so on without any tools easily.
  • Multi-Purpose and Perfect Gift: The hat storage organizer is not only suitable for baseball caps but also can be used to storage purses, snacks, scarves, towels, tissues, diapers, toys and so on. Its a great gift for your families or friends who loves collecting hats or keeping organized.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
